`\n  Line 106: - [ ] **TASK-018**: Implement `update_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, updates: Dict[str, Any]) -> AgentMetadata` in `MetadataService`\n  Line 111: - [ ] **TASK-019**: Implement `validate_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path) -> bool` in `MetadataService`\n  Line 116: - [ ] **TASK-020**: Implement `_validate_python_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata)` in `MetadataService`\n  Line 120: - [ ] **TASK-021**: Implement `_validate_java_workspace(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata)` in `MetadataService`\n  Line 359: #### MetadataService Tests\n  Line 364: - [ ] **TEST-011**: Implement `TestMetadataService.test_load_metadata_success` in `test_metadata_service.py`\n  Line 369: - [ ] **TEST-012**: Implement `TestMetadataService.test_load_metadata_fallback` in `test_metadata_service.py`\n  Line 373: - [ ] **TEST-013**: Implement `TestMetadataService.test_load_metadata_not_found` in `test_metadata_service.py`\n  Line 377: - [ ] **TEST-014**: Implement `TestMetadataService.test_save_metadata` in `test_metadata_service.py`\n  Line 382: - [ ] **TEST-015**: Implement `TestMetadataService.test_validate_language` in `test_metadata_service.py`\n  Line 386: - [ ] **TEST-016**: Implement `TestMetadataService.test_validate_build_mode` in `test_metadata_service.py`\n  Line 390: - [ ] **TEST-017**: Implement `TestMetadataService.test_validate_port_range` in `test_metadata_service.py`\n  Line 428:   - MetadataService class and methods\n  Line 631: 2. **MetadataService Tests**: Validate metadata loading, saving, validation\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z/changes/AR-020/proposal.md:\n  Line 94: │   │   ├── metadata_service.py # MetadataService, AgentMetadata\n  Line 108:     ├── test_metadata_service.py # MetadataService tests\n  Line 261: class MetadataService:\n  Line 394: from agentcube.services.metadata_service import AgentMetadata, MetadataService\n  Line 4